{"tid":37390,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"【改詞MV】[你的名字] 女版 夢燈籠 粵語","createTime":"2016-12-13T10:04:57.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-22T01:50:41.000Z","uid":48498,"like":9,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4208103a6c15f819036f2c238d1b9a7f6879be82","tid":37390,"uid":48498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T10:04:57.000Z","msg":"燈籠Cantonese Girl Ver.<br />\n<br />\n主唱：可兒 kani music<br />\n詞：大豬包包<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/msaAoXvtdRI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FmsaAoXvtdRI&d=J2CQx%2BDwjwZH88hWyggv3UsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=76f0e07d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/msaAoXvtdRI</a><br />\n<br />\n如果 聲音 不消失 可於腦海記得<br />\n如此 就可 尋遍這地球 去找你 夢裏漫遊<br />\n如果 夢境 就此 編織到可永久 <br />\n未怕天給你我這個毒咒 我也總可 去挽留你這對手<br />\n就再抖擻 我倆在這個節奏<br />\n覓個出口 不顫抖 去走<br />\n<br />\nOh<br />\n<br />\n快 聽見我倆碰見心中急速那心跳聲<br />\n來再去挽手觀望著日落命運回應<br />\n尋遍了世間這感應<br />\n無限時間地形 無用問那姓名 <br />\n你 那會夠勇氣 喝我那口嚼後無聲<br />\n你笑笑看 我那臉型<br />\n和~你 去挽救這世界日月連繩<br />\n回望着那過程 流著淚的溫馨<br />\n<br />\n未怕世間多少分秒 去覓你姓名<br />\n在我掌心寫出一句 愛着你記認<br />\n暴風中帶著我手繩打拼 <br />\n糸守中 看着我掌心和應<br />\n為着了去兌現 你與我心的伏線<br />\n維持着我笑臉 那怕世間改變"},{"pid":"101375c2249d11d8ffb7ffdf031c2b922102dd22","tid":37390,"uid":1893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T10:06:00.000Z","msg":"光速推post"},{"pid":"4082f5b7e9081aa58008869af48b6c292c73f3d4","tid":37390,"uid":2350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T10:10:03.000Z","msg":"好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ead8ec071a84f3233d7edabdf06620a1b0d665a1","tid":37390,"uid":7212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T10:15:38.000Z","msg":"正皮支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4f4694beb2f18d0422ff64822b4862e816681e7","tid":37390,"uid":26878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T10:16:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/fac